database.name: VIEW SWA_INOUT_RELATION_VOID_V
database.view: SELECT COALESCE(io.m_inout_id, '-') || rio.m_inout_id AS swa_inout_relation_void_v_id, io.ad_client_id, io.ad_org_id, io.isactive, io.updated, io.updatedby, io.created, io.createdby, io.m_inout_id, io.documentno, max(tr.trxprocessdate) AS trxprocessdate, rio.m_inout_id AS m_inout_source_if, rio.documentno AS documentno_source, rio.em_scr_physical_documentno, max(io.created + '00:00:00.001') AS trxprocessdate_source FROM m_inoutline iol JOIN m_transaction tr ON tr.m_inoutline_id = iol.m_inoutline_id JOIN m_inout io ON io.m_inout_id = iol.m_inout_id JOIN m_inoutline riol ON riol.m_inoutline_id = iol.canceled_inoutline_id JOIN m_transaction rtr ON rtr.m_inoutline_id = riol.m_inoutline_id JOIN m_inout rio ON rio.m_inout_id = riol.m_inout_id WHERE io.docstatus = 'VO' GROUP BY io.m_inout_id, io.ad_client_id, io.ad_org_id, io.isactive, io.updated, io.updatedby, io.created, io.createdby, io.documentno, rio.m_inout_id, rio.documentno, rio.em_scr_physical_documentno
